{"tid":1791084,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"曱甴：對於有人在網上發起報復行動 警方不會姑息任何影響市民的行為","createTime":"2019-12-20T13:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T15:06:45.000Z","uid":216992,"like":31,"dislike":122,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"0eeb477b4d94b85730899419d9de531cd68eba71","tid":1791084,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T13:25:33.000Z","msg":"警方：留意到有人就「星火同盟」案在網上發起報復行動<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，屬於支援被捕者組織「星火同盟」的3男1女已獲准保釋候查，須於明年1月中旬向警方報到。警方在社交網站發布短片，表示留意到有人就這宗案件，在網上發起報復行動，包括破壞提供戶口的銀行和在聖誕節到各大商場大肆破壞，指出<span style=\"color: red;\">這些行為比黑社會行徑更卑劣</span>，相信市民希望在冬至和聖誕見到和平日子，警方不會姑息任何影響市民的行為。警方同時交代上月兩宗刑事毀壞案件中，共拘捕10人，分別涉嫌破壞東涌一個商場的商舖和馬鞍山港鐵站，其中4名被捕人士是中學生。警方又說<span style=\"color: red;\">年輕人忽視守法意識，令人擔憂</span>，會全力追查案件，不會讓犯罪者逍遙法外。<br />\n<br />\n2019-12-20 21:17:44"},{"pid":"d9e1d04ce4c124b0ffbeb4f43b1b72c36c89ee57","tid":1791084,"uid":216992,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T13:27:18.000Z","msg":"唔知係邊個忽視守法意識呢何<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597792a96b5cc52fb050fa88692a219b67818f02","tid":1791084,"uid":1891,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n1221<br />\n多謝黨鐵開啟721紀念日通知<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccF7Pwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccF7Pwj.jpg&h=a4c97012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XcqBbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XcqBbk.png&h=b08a4737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEkp4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPEkp4G.jpg&h=82652877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23c1e4eeb32b05a6cd1c86bfcee46d7f9de81c96","tid":1791084,"uid":88940,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12